name: #2 AGONY
description: One must break the seal of immortality to reach the twisted mind of the old one called Agony. As hunters broke through, the veil to the other side was lifted and the horrors of purgatory entered the human realm. A vicious war of the undead rained down on humanity, with lives replaced by corpses and screams swallowed whole by hellhounds howling through the everlasting nights.
